bors d+
I guess the lack of WithTop here means you can't reuse the new lemma for one direction?
No, I do reuse the new lemma for one direction. In fact, the new lemma is just one implication of the old lemma, which happens to hold with a more general assumption (`WithTop ℕ∞` instead of `ℕ∞`)
It strikes me as a bit odd that these statements are not applied further, but fine if this is more useful. (Or maybe have both?)
Indeed, the unapplied version is useful in the proof, but I agree the applied version is maybe more natural. I've added both.
